# CosmicBoard Web Application

A cosmic-themed task and reference management system built with Next.js and MongoDB.

## Related Projects
- **Mobile Version**: ~/Projects/cosmicboard-mobile
  - React Native app with local storage
  - Shares data models and business logic
  - Uses same JSON structure for compatibility
  - Premium IAP for web sync functionality

## Important Notes
- When making changes to data models or core features, consider updating both web and mobile versions
- The web version uses MongoDB for data persistence
- Mobile app will sync with this web version via premium IAP
- Maintain feature parity where possible between platforms

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15.3.4 with App Router
- MongoDB with Mongoose
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- SWR for data fetching

## Features
- Project management
- Task tracking with cosmic priorities (SUPERNOVA, STELLAR, NEBULA)
- Reference storage (code snippets and documentation)
- Tags and search functionality
- Markdown support with syntax highlighting
- Export/Import functionality

## Development
```bash
npm run dev      # Start development server on port 7777
npm run build    # Build for production
npm run start    # Start production server
```

## Access
- Local: http://localhost:7777
- Domain: http://cosmic.board (via nginx reverse proxy)